data.description: Come see this great 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home. With a bright open floor plan and tile throughout you'll love coming home everyday. This home also has a solar system that will help save money on those electric bills. Close to Palm Springs, shopping and great restaurants all you need is at your finger tips. Don't miss out, this home is easy to see, schedule your showing today.
